item.title: Alert
item.description:
29/06 Technical issues
The realm Zenedar is currently experiencing some technical issues. Due to this, players on the affected realms may be disconnected or experience latency. The issues are being addressed and will be resolved as soon as possible.
We apologise for any inconvenience this may cause.
